# guides : common problems faced during archinstall


# issue : unable to start gui or launch dwm
reason : missign gpu drivers
first : if you want to install gpu drivers automatically then choose xorg in profiles

# issue : no audio on fresh install
reason : need to setup

paru/yay -S asoundconf
asoundconf list
asoundconf set-default-card AUDIO_DEVICE
alsamixer -c 0 # unmute the audio device

 pactl set-sink-volume @DEFAULT_SINK@ 50%  #set
 pactl set-sink-volume @DEFAULT_SINK@ -5%  # dec
 pactl set-sink-volume @DEFAULT_SINK@ +5%  # inc



